name: Operation Neptune (Dinamic Software)
overview: An unpublished shooter from Narciso Quintana that was to be published by Dinamic Software, except, as he was underage, his parents would not sign off on the contract. The game was by Narisco but the graphics were property of Dinamic so the game could not be finished. it only ever got as far as a simple test demo, with a score panel, enemies and a looping map. So enjoy a glimpse of a Dinamic game that never was.
